{{Top|leg}}
The '''Malio Preserve Units''' were facilities that contain alpha, beta, secondary, and tertiary copies of every creature or being the [[Kaminoan/Legends|Kaminoans]] ever [[Cloning/Legends|cloned]], bred, intended to clone, or examined. The Preserve Units were attached to [[Tipoca City/Legends|Tipoca City]], but could be separated and isolated in case of a breakout and to protect the samples from each other.

